- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses hyperparameter tuning and combining different regularizations, which are common topics in machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with neural networks, which are a popular tool in AI research. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper focuses on neural networks, but it is less likely than the previous categories as the paper does not explicitly discuss evolutionary computing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on image or video data, which are common in computer vision research.
